c: 35
v: 40
t: "Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ese ntimubona ibigirwamana byanyu musenga bitari Allah? Nimunyereke icyo byaremye ku isi. Ese byaba byaragize uruhare mu iremwa ry’ibirere, cyangwa ngo tube twarabahaye igitabo bakaba ari cyo bakomoramo ibimenyetso bigaragara bagenderaho? (Oya!) Ahubwo ibyo ababangikanyamana bamwe basezeranya abandi ni ibinyoma"